Package org.azyva.dragom.execcontext.plugin.impl

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DefaultCredentialStorePluginImpl
    This default implementation of CredentialStorePlugin uses CredentialStore to manage credentials.
    DefaultEventPluginImpl
    Default EventPlugin implementation.
    DefaultRuntimePropertiesPluginImpl
    This default implementation of RuntimePropertiesPlugin considers the following sources for the properties, in precedence order (the first one that provides a requested property is used): Transient data within the ExecContext (ExecContext.getTransientData(java.lang.String)) Tool properties (ToolLifeCycleExecContext.getToolProperty(java.lang.String)), if the ExecContext implements ToolLifeCycleExecContext ExecContext properties (ExecContext.getProperty(java.lang.String)) ExecContext initialization properties (ExecContext.getInitProperty(java.lang.String)) Node properties within the Model (@link Node#getProperty}.
